name: Come Lazy Go Crazy
about: 3 Rounds. Round 1: One member will be given a word and should say it out loud, the other persons will keep headphones and guess the word. Round 2: A player holds the loop in one hand and attempts to guide it along the curved wire without touching the loop. Round 3: Person should blow the ballon and burst without using hands

name: Digi Quest
about: Check your Luck in round 1 show your skill in round 2 Cross these levels to play the most exiting and adventurous treasure hunt using QR codes. Scan QR codes to find the hidden treasure

name: Granny's House
about: This is about a person who has a grandmother would not let her out of the house. You have to let her grand daughter escape the house without getting caught. You will lose if she catches you
